{"type": "article", "id": 26210, "title": "果汁包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-29T07:23:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 176, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132731tGd9XpR7bEJTuBPK.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">在到底该如何表现果汁的新鲜程度上，<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://backbonebranding.com/\">Backbone Branding</a> 有一套自己的想法：这个为 Siya 系列果汁所设计的包装，好像就是一个真实水果被放在了果汁瓶上。巧妙的弧线造型配合精心策划后实际拍摄出的照片，使得它在众多果汁包装中脱颖而出，很好地反映出了“天然”的感觉，像是锁住了盛夏的味道。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132728T3f81A2IajRvmDKU.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.47476341\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132730oVG3lH6ZFrw7xbg9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132730xwfETD8NUO0l2yJS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132730FqphwK39OYPBlb0T.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}